Typing Speed Tester

A simple web-based typing speed tester built with HTML, CSS, and vanilla JavaScript.
It fetches random quotes from an API and allows users to test their typing speed and accuracy for a selected duration.

Features

Select test duration: 30s, 60s, or 90s.

Fetches random quotes from baconipsum API
.

Tracks time remaining, WPM (words per minute), and accuracy (%).

Input is disabled until duration is selected.

Test stops automatically when the time ends or quote is completed.

Restart test at any time with a new quote.

Technologies Used

HTML – Structure of the page.

CSS – Styling with a gradient background and responsive layout.

JavaScript (Vanilla) – Handles typing logic, API fetch, timer, and stats.

API – baconipsum for generating text.
